oldiers halted two German plain clothes men from the American Zone near the sector border stabbed one beat the other with a rifle butt and carried them into the Soviet Zone bodily when they refused to cross the line Two German policemen of the British sector were the others kid naped One escaped and the Brit ish are demanding return of the second The Russians yesterday seized five policemen from the Ameri can Zone Two of them have es caped The Americans have asked"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2024-05-22T13:01:07.725Z", "group": ["ndnp/ak", "alaska-state-library-historical-collections-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn83045499/1948-08-21/ed-1/?sp=1", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ak:batch_ak_junco_ver01:data:sn83045499:00514154430:1948082101:0323/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=416&w=325", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ak:batch_ak_junco_ver01:data:sn83045499:00514154430:1948082101:0323/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=832&w=651", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/ak/batch_ak_junco_ver01/data/sn83045499/00514154430/1948082101/0323.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 1, "language": ["english"], "location": ["juneau", "alaska", "united states"], "location_city": ["juneau"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_county": ["juneau"], "location_state": ["alaska"], "mime_type": ["image/jp2", "application/pdf", "text/xml", "image/jpeg", "image/jpeg", "application/json", "text/plain"], "number": ["5", "0", "3", "4", "0000000001", "sn83045499", "1"], "number_edition": ["1"], "number_lccn": ["sn83045499"], "number_page": ["0000000001"], "number_reel": ["0", "0", "5", "1", "4", "1", "5", "4", "4", "3", "0"], "online_format": ["image", "pdf", "online text"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["the daily alaska empire (juneau, alaska) 1926-1964", "chronicling america", "serial and government publications div